  "body": "As a follow up to #8179 we should not be relying on system tags to figure out a contact's (request) state.\r\nThe linked PR introduces the `ContactRequestState` enum which should be relied on instead.\r\n\r\nSo this task is about removing the usage/dependence on `hasAddedUs`, `added`, etc and replace them with corresponding `ContactRequestState` values.",
