    "body": "As mentioned in https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/8179#issuecomment-1310406647 this needs clarification from UX/UI.\r\n\r\nIn desktop, changing to exclusively using ContactRequestState will cause \"breaking\" UI changes (re-sent contact requests won't show up anymore because the requestState will not be updated if it was dismissed/rejected once).\r\n\r\nNeed to check if this is desired.",
